categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Some years before the Cold War, a female Jedi attempted to rescue Tythan Phomm from a group of Morgukai warriors. Unknown to her, Phomm was in no danger and was merely used by the Nikto a bait to lure her in. The Morgukai killed the Jedi and then let Phomm go, though the experience made him abhor the Morgukai for years to come.
